<subSubSection id="7199C8799540F3B8E1715D9ED66F4343" pageId="0" pageNumber="53" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="B75CD05D3990F79BA1416D1954C3AE2E" pageId="0" pageNumber="53">
<taxonomicName id="D8428EE9F105DB2E96548F25A02C8B72" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Jotus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Jotus" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Jotus</taxonomicName>
L. Koch, 1881a: 1243. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="0E02287E6A37BEF7013D1B02F84D5AF5" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Jotus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Jotus auripes" order="Araneae" pageId="0" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="auripes">Jotus auripes</taxonomicName>
